      <div class="current-roles" id="current-roles">
          <section class="role_appointment role" id="role_appointment_1501">
            <h1 id="director-general-international-and-eu">Director General, International and EU </h1>
            <div class="govspeak">
<p>Responsibilities include:</p>

<ul>
  <li>the delivery of HM Treasury’s work programme, in particular supporting the government’s objectives to promote macroeconomic stability and maintain confidence in the macro policy framework - to promote stability, fairness, efficiency and competitiveness in financial markets and to promote sustainable economic growth</li>
  <li>leading the Treasury’s relationships with foreign finance ministries and central banks, international and EU institutions, Foreign & Commonwealth Office and Cabinet Office (European and Global Issues Secretariat)</li>
</ul>
</div>
            <div class="read-more">
                <p class="js-hide-other-departments organisations-name-list">
  <a class="organisation-link" href="/government/organisations/hm-treasury">HM Treasury</a>
</p>

            </div>
</section>      </div>

